PrecisApproval of the appointment by the Minister of Transport of LOUIS RANGER of Gatineau, Quebec, as a director of the Board of Directors of Canada Mortgage and Housing Corporation, selected from the public service of Canada, to hold office during pleasure for a term of three years, in the place of Janice Cochrane, whose term has expired.
